  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Join the Pancake Patrol - A Delicious Fusion of Bullet Heaven and Bullet Hell!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an epic quest to <strong>deliver pancakes to Pembrook's Manor</strong> in this action-packed roguelite. <strong>Recruit companions</strong> and battle through hordes of monsters with your arsenal of culinary weapons, facing off against <strong>unique bullet hell bosses</strong> with challenging mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2587840/extras/f452edd7cf1c01384ac26ca5ad13ad43.poster.avif?t=1773674817\" width=642 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2587840/extras/f452edd7cf1c01384ac26ca5ad13ad43.webm?t=1773674817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2587840/extras/f452edd7cf1c01384ac26ca5ad13ad43.mp4?t=1773674817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into <strong>bullet hell battles</strong> where you become the storm, in a pancake-themed roguelite. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Recruit Companions to fight alongside you</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2587840/extras/72be19c479be5a16290af6a53b0cfef6.avif?t=1773674817\" width=1560 height=842 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover and mix <strong>food-based weapons</strong> like the <strong>Whip(ped) Cream</strong> and <strong>Maple Syrup Tornado</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2587840/extras/2196271a66b82ff84fc732b7167ad24d.avif?t=1773674817\" width=1120 height=974 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into <strong>thrilling game modes</strong> like the adrenaline-pumping <strong>Boss Rush with 10 epic showdowns</strong>, the chaotic <strong>Horde Mode</strong> with wild modifiers, the heart-racing <strong>Bacon Rush</strong> where you dodge sizzling bacon bullets unarmed, the intense <strong>True Bullet Hell</strong> where you weave through a storm of projectiles, and the exhilarating <strong>Bullet Heaven</strong> classic!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from <strong>10 unique characters</strong>, each offering a different playstyle and abilities.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2587840/extras/1a9a1ef5b498422f78c8790ddbfa58c6.poster.avif?t=1773674817\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2587840/extras/1a9a1ef5b498422f78c8790ddbfa58c6.webm?t=1773674817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2587840/extras/1a9a1ef5b498422f78c8790ddbfa58c6.mp4?t=1773674817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your skills in <strong>1v1 boss fights</strong>, mastering each boss's patterns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete on the <strong>Leaderboards</strong> and unlock <strong>Steam Achievements</strong> to prove your prowess.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Join the Pancake Patrol - A Delicious Fusion of Bullet Heaven and Bullet Hell!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an epic quest to <strong>deliver pancakes to Pembrook's Manor</strong> in this action-packed roguelite. <strong>Recruit companions</strong> and battle through hordes of monsters with your arsenal of culinary weapons, facing off against <strong>unique bullet hell bosses</strong> with challenging mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2587840/extras/f452edd7cf1c01384ac26ca5ad13ad43.poster.avif?t=1773674817\" width=642 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2587840/extras/f452edd7cf1c01384ac26ca5ad13ad43.webm?t=1773674817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2587840/extras/f452edd7cf1c01384ac26ca5ad13ad43.mp4?t=1773674817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into <strong>bullet hell battles</strong> where you become the storm, in a pancake-themed roguelite. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Recruit Companions to fight alongside you</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2587840/extras/72be19c479be5a16290af6a53b0cfef6.avif?t=1773674817\" width=1560 height=842 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover and mix <strong>food-based weapons</strong> like the <strong>Whip(ped) Cream</strong> and <strong>Maple Syrup Tornado</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" sr